IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.D_STMDPeople') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.D_STMDPeople
GO

    [md_people_physicalunitpostalnumber] nvarchar(4000),
    [md_people_postaladdressid] nvarchar(4000),

    [md_people_postalblock] nvarchar(4000),

	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Structured Data/MD/stmdpeople.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO
